s.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33914,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/12\/charity-on-behalf-of-parents\/","url_meta":{"origin":43669,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqa: Charity on behalf of deceases parents is rewarded","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 12, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, my mother died suddenly without writing a will. I think if she could speak, she would give in charity. Will she have a reward if I give charity on\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18997,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/06\/all-involved-rewarded-sadaqah\/","url_meta":{"origin":43669,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqa: All involved in charity are rewarded","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 6, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen a woman spends in charity from the food of her house, without wasting it, she will have a reward from what she spent. Her husband will have a reward from what he earned, and the storekeeper\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1758,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/12\/22\/plant-tree-re